   &UR; FANNIE-FREDDIE-FRAUD-ECONOMIST &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   Fannie and Freddie sound like a sweet couple living down the
street. But in America they are more likely to own the mortgage on
your and your neighbors' house. For Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac are
two of America's biggest financial institutions _ and also two of
its most indebted, with around $1 trillion of debt between them. &QL;
