<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Caregiver stress comes in many forms
 &HT;    By Hap LeCrone
 &HT;    c. 2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   WACO, Texas _ In the past, long-term caregiving was a relatively
