<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-14 13:20 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6787 &Cx1f; ttj-z
r k BC-SALTER-COLUMN-HNS &LR;      04-14 0784
