</P>
<P>
   VEEP-KERRY (Washington) _ US Sen. John Kerry is being talked of
by knowledgeable insiders as a serious contender for vice
president. By Jill Zuckman. 795 words.
</P>
<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   MA-SLAVE-MEMORIAL (Medford, Mass.) _ It's not much to look at,
the old brick wall. But to some, the crumbling wall built in 1765
by an African slave named Pomp is perhaps the finest candidate for
a proper memorial to slavery that Massachusetts has to offer. By
Ralphael Lewis. 1200 words. PHOTO
</P>
