what it is, I often have to shut down my computer after it locks
up. When it boots back up, Norton Disk Doctor starts to run in DOS.
I really don't want this to run and check all my files. It takes
forever. How can I prevent it?'' Assorted Q&AMP;As. By DWIGHT
SILVERMAN.
