presidential candidates stand on the issues, we should find out
what their aspirations are for themselves and our country. So far
neither Al Gore nor George W. Bush has been able to articulate
those values or give speeches that would lift the soul of America.
By ROBERT E. THOMPSON. (Filed Wednesday.)
