<HEADLINE>
&HT;     GOVERNMENT TO ADVISE TEENS AGAINST STEROID USE 
</HEADLINE>
   &HT;     (EDS: Filed in the ``w'' and ``s'' categories)  
 &HT;     (For use by New York Times News Service clients.)  
 &HT;     By AUSTIN ZALKIN  
 &HT;     c.2000 Hearst Newspapers  
