<P>
   MARKET-WORST (Undated) _ CMGI, Akamai, Sycamore -- for a year,
these three companies have been linked as the vanguard of the new
economy. This week, the market turned, and each company's stock was
chopped in half. By Hiawatha Bray. 800 words.
