<P>
   &UR; NATIONAL (a) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   CUBA-BOY (Miami) _ Relatives of Elian Gonzalez argue in federal
court that he should not leave the country until the United States
can certify that his human rights won't be violated in Cuba. By
Adam Pertman.
</P>
<P>
   w/
</P>
<P>
   WALKER-COLUMN (Miami) _ By Adrian Walker.
