<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-04-14 20:33 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A7419 &Cx1f; taf-z
u f BC-DOTCOM-LOSSES-ART-NYT     04-14 1180
