<TEXT>
<P>
   Attention graphics editors, the following market graphics have
moved Friday 04/14/00:
</P>
<P>
   MARKET_Debt growth -- 2 x 3 1/2 -- (BC-MARKET-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Growth rate of debt in margin accounts at its highest level in a
decade.
</P>
<P>
   MARKET_Activity 0415 -- 2 x 3 -- (BC-MARKET-NYT)
</P>
<P>
   Friday's stock free fall at a glance; Chart of Nasdaq over this
week. Pdf file; posted only.
</P>
<P>
