<P>
   BIZ-PRELUDES (Undated) _ Now college students are being required
to bring their laptops to class, but there they often spend their
time trading emails, trading stocks or surfing. At some schools,
though, the professor can cut everyone off with the press of a
button. By Abby Ellin. (Moved).  &QL; 
 &QL;
</P>
